    "summary": "Maersk exposes multiple HTTP APIs for logistics and ground freight on api.maersk.com and pilotdelivers.com, authenticated either with a Developer Portal Consumer Key alone for some APIs, OAuth 2.0 client-credentials plus `Consumer-Key` for newer Ground Freight APIs, or legacy Ground Freight User ID/password for at least the Tracking API, while some older SOAP-style services have undocumented/unclear auth.",
    "credentials": {
      "maersk_consumer_key": {
        "type": "api_key",
        "label": "Maersk Consumer Key",
        "generateUrl": "https://developer.maersk.com/register",
        "setup": "Create a Developer Portal account at [Maersk Developer Portal registration](https://developer.maersk.com/register), then in the portal create an integration/app. The portal generates a `Consumer Key` automatically, and from the app's update screen you can copy, revoke, or add consumer keys. Some customer APIs require an official company email and at least one Maersk customer code, as described in [Getting Started API](https://developer.maersk.com/support/getting-started-api)."
      },
      "maersk_client_credentials": {
        "type": "oauth2_cc",
        "label": "Maersk OAuth client credentials",
        "generateUrl": "https://developer.maersk.com/register",
        "setup": "Create a Developer Portal account and app via [Maersk Developer Portal registration](https://developer.maersk.com/register). Select the API products your app will use. For APIs that require OAuth 2.0, access is granted after approval; once enabled, use the app's `client_id` and `client_secret` to request tokens from `https://api.maersk.com/customer-identity/oauth/v2/access_token` or the stage equivalent. The portal's support docs say OAuth-enabled products may take up to 10 business days for approval, and the Ground Freight docs note to contact your Maersk sales representative for credentials. See [Getting Started API](https://developer.maersk.com/support/getting-started-api) and [Ratings API](https://delivers.maersk.com/developer/apis/ratings/)."
      },
      "mgf_basic_user": {
        "type": "basic",
        "label": "Maersk Ground Freight user ID and password",
        "setup": "Obtain a Maersk Ground Freight / CoPilot account and API access through your Maersk sales representative or from your CoPilot account settings as described in [Maersk Web Services & APIs](https://delivers.maersk.com/developer/) and the [Tracking API](https://delivers.maersk.com/developer/apis/tracking/). The docs state these legacy services use a `User ID` and `Password` for authentication."
      }
    },
